These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: baking, dancing, hiking, reading, singing
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, manager, scientist, nurse, bartender
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
There 5 different types of food: peas, radish, cauliflower, tomato, pepper
 1. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person eating pepper is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person eating radish is on the right of the designer##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the right of the scientist##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the nurse##1
 6. the manager is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 8. the manager is on the far left##1
 9. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the manager##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating peas##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person eating peas##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | baking    | reading | hiking    | singing  |
| Job   | manager  | designer | scientist | nurse | bartender  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Food         | cauliflower | tomato    | radish | peas  | pepper |

