.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
There 5 different types of food: artichoke, cucumber, kiwi, lettuce, watermelon
5 different games are played: domino, monopoly, chess, bridge, canasta
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: adventure, animation, documentary, family, martial-arts
5 different pets are kept: rat, chinchilla, fish, snake, goldfish
 1. the person playing bridge is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 2. the owner of the fish is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 6. the person playing chess is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 8. the person eating kiwi is the person watching documentary movies##1
 9. the owner of the snake is the person eating kiwi##1
10. the person eating cucumber is in the middle##1
11. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
12. the person eating kiwi is the person playing monopoly##1
13. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Food          | kiwi        | watermelon | cucumber     | lettuce      | artichoke  |
| Game           | monopoly   | chess | canasta    | bridge | domino |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | family     | martial-arts | adventure    | animation  |
| Pet   | snake     | chinchilla | rat    | goldfish      | fish    |

