.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
The people have 5 different hobbies: cooking, magic-tricks, reading, traveling, writing
The people have 5 different jobs:  firefighter, electrician, videographer, librarian, social-worker
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: trance, funk, hip-hop, classical, punk
 1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the social-worker##1
 2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 3. the firefighter is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the videographer is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
 7. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 8. the videographer is on the right of the librarian##1
 9. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
10. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the electrician##1
11. the videographer is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the electrician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing | traveling  | reading   | cooking    |
| Job   | electrician        | social-worker | firefighter | librarian    | videographer   |
| Music-Genre     | trance   | hip-hop | punk      | funk | classical |

