.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
There 5 different types of food: kale, lemon, papaya, plum, zucchini
The people have 5 different hobbies: augustd-games, rock-climbing, baking, writing, chess
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, gospel, indie, pop, techno
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, august, july, november, april
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the person who's hobby is augustd-games is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is augustd-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's hobby is augustd-games##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person eating kale##1
10. the person eating zucchini is the fan of indie##1
11. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1
12. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food          | plum        | kale       | papaya | lemon   | zucchini  |
| Hobby   | chess | baking | rock-climbing | augustd-games   | writing |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | techno     | gospel | country | indie     |
| Birthday     | december        | august        | april    | november    | july      |

