.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, cauliflower, nectarine, potato, pumpkin
The people use 5 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, van, motorbike, bike
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, poppy, iris, daisy, dahlia
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, sailing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who growspoppy is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person driving the van##1
 3. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 4. the person eating potato is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 7. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person who growsdahlia is in the middle##1
 9. the person eating cauliflower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
10. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
11. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
12. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Food          | cauliflower    | pumpkin  | nectarine | asparagus    | potato      |
| Transport           | bike | van | boat  | motorbike | helicopter |
