5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, pall-mall, game, tiparillo, montecristo
 1. the pilot is on the left of the person eating banana##1
 2. the game-smoker is the freelancer##1
 3. the person eating raspberry is in the middle##1
 4. the designer is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far right##1
 6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is in the middle##1
 8. the person eating lettuce is on the left of the pilot##1
 9. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the engineer##1
10. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the right of the person eating raspberry##1
11. the designer is the person eating cherry##1
12. the tiparillo-smoker is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
13. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |     5     |
| Food          | cherry     | lettuce  | raspberry | banana     | artichoke |
