 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
10. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching romance movies is the person who's birthday is in october##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Transport      | skateboard      | snowmobile       | roller         | boat  | quad-bike |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | martial-arts | crime  | western  |
| Birthday   | october    | february    | december        | july | june     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

