.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: white, azure, lilac, black, green
The people use 5 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, motorbike, ship, airplane
5 different pets are kept: bird, dog, fish, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, sailing, swimming, volleyball
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person who likes green##1
 7. the person who likes azure is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 8. the person who likes lilac is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 9. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the bird is the person driving the airplane##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
12. the person who likes green is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
13. the person who likes black is the person driving the airplane##1

