 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 8. the person traveling to miami is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is in the middle##1
10. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the fan of blues is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
12. the fan of rock is the person drinking tea##1
