.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, milk, mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: blues, country, pop, punk, salsa
There 5 different types of food: lime, kiwi, pepper, carrot, artichoke
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, pall-mall, alhambra, oliveros, vegafina
 1. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the prince-smoker##1
 3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the person eating artichoke##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the fan of pop is the person eating kiwi##1
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the person eating lime is the person drinking mirinda##1
14. the person eating carrot is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | mirinda   | milk    | cola       | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | pop           | country   | salsa   | punk       | blues  |
| Food   | kiwi       | lime | pepper | carrot     | artichoke   |
| Cigar     | alhambra    | pall-mall   | oliveros   | prince | vegafina   |

 